            <h2>About The Owner</h2>
            <p>
                Vector Electric Corporation is owned by David Bensel, who has worked in the electrical field since 1987.
                He became a journeyman electrician in 1991 and received his master’s license in 2007. David started his
                company with his business partner as J&D Electrical in 2009, and rebranded as Vector Electric in 2014.
                During that time, Vector Electric has been proud to offer its customers an excellent level of service
                in every aspect of electrical contracting.
            </p>
        </div>
