<div class="container">
    <h1 class="text-center">Services</h1>
    <div class="container">
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-4">content</div>
            <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h2>Residential Electric</h2>
                <p>
                    Vector Electric is your custom electrical design specialist. Whether your project is a custom home
                    or a large subdivision, we can do it all for new construction, remodels, tenant improvement, and underground
                    electrical installations. We will come to your site to install high voltage electrical systems, wire up low
                    voltage systems such as alarms or communication lines, install access control systems, and install fire
                    alarm systems. We also offer installation of site lighting, street lighting, and much more to suit your home’s
                    specific needs.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-8">
                <h2>Commercial Electric</h2>
                <p>
                    When it comes to commercial electrical, Vector Electric is your one-stop shop. We can service any size of
                    business or commercial structure, from small offices to 500,000 square foot spaces. We offer high and low voltage
                    wiring, communication lines, access control systems, fire alarm systems, building automation systems, and much more.
                    We also provide lighting design, whether you’re looking to brighten up a workspace or create a dimmer, more romantic
                    restaurant atmosphere.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4 text-center">
                <ul>
